description:
Shannon Kelly returns to US after being absent in Season two. Shannon (lifetime 3-0) was Season one’s Featherweight Champion. A fan favorite, Shannon announced her decision to return in our forums and posted this comment
I noticed a few new girls in my weight class that look like they could be fun matches, but I have no doubt that I will win each and every match that I am in, and have fun doing it! …Looking forward to kickin ass in season 3!!!
. Kat gives it her all but in the end Shannon’s experience and strength turn little Kat into a helpless kitten on the mat.
title: WELCOME TO THE START OF SEASON THREE! Shannon Kelly(0-0) vs Kat (0-0)
